Inheritance: Is A relation.
			 parent & child classes ( super & sub)

			class A  extends Class B

			child class (sub): inherits the variables and methods
			(Visible to the child class) from parent class (super)

			parent class (super): can not inherit anything from child
			 (sub class)



protected access modifier: Alayws visible within the same package
						   Visible outside the package in subclass
						    ONLY
Final Keyword: Unchangable


